name: LifeTrip
0:
”Alexa, start Life Trip”
”Alexa, open Life Trip”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: life trip
des:
Do you miss those innocent days of your childhood? Or are you a child, who wants to see what awaits for him once he gets older? Well, it's not every day when you are powered to relive your past, cherish your present, and see your future. But, with this Alexa skill, everything is possible!

Choose a life stage, answer to difficult and fun choices, and bear the good or bad consequences it comes with. Your anonymous life is in your own hands! 
Now, it's up to you, whether it would be a long or a short one!

Currently, we have three life stages - 
Childhood
Middle age
Teenage
Simply pick one stage, and start your Life Trip!
